@startuml
title Dashboard Due-Step Computation — Activity Diagram

start
:Load patients & journeys;
:For each patient: collect
ALL PatientJourney records
(may be multiple parallel journeys);
:For each ACTIVE/SUSPENDED journey:
Apply pause shift
(totalPausedDays + currentPauseDays);
:Apply modifications per journey
(ADD_STEP, REMOVE_STEP);
:Overlay research module
entries if researchModuleIds
are present;
:Compute effective steps per journey
(getEffectiveSteps);
:Resolve patient instructions
from persisted Instruction
records;
:Merge & deduplicate due steps
across parallel journeys by
templateId
(getMergedDueStepsForPatient);
:Map merged steps to
queue/category;
:Build dashboard Case rows
with computed category
and nextStep;
stop

@enduml
